headline: CBTS Announces Comprehensive Technology Solutions for University of Kentucky to Support Infrastructure Modernization
summary: CINCINNATI, February 18, 2026--CBTS, a leading provider of managed IT and networking solutions, has entered into a contract agreement with the University of Kentucky to deliver a full suite of technology services to modernize and future-proof the institution’s infrastructure.
